  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you have fit your armor with a special chakra visor that grants you 60 feet of Darkvision and doubles your normal sight range.</p><p> If you already have Darkvision, it is increased by 60 feet instead.</p><p> You can accurately make out the details of things within 1 mile of you.</p><p> Also at 6th level, you learn the E-Rank Ninjutsu Enhanced Defense.</p><p> When you take the attack action, you can cast Enhanced Defense at the conclusion of your attack action.</p><p></p>",
